The Vice President emphasized the importance of getting vaccinated and stated that vaccines will save lives. She mentioned the heartbreaking experience of seeing people on their deathbeds, begging others to get vaccinated. The Vice President urged everyone to get vaccinated to avoid putting their loved ones through such a situation. She commended the efforts of the governor, mayor, county executive, and congressmember in New Jersey for their work in promoting vaccination. The Vice President emphasized the need to continue the vaccination efforts and not give up.